{"tid":186283,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"作左幾首歌想發圍應該點做？","createTime":"2017-04-04T05:54:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-09T09:12:19.000Z","uid":31173,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a1313d513b3b0cbc83d8de8ddb870e6517fe5104","tid":186283,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T05:54:17.000Z","msg":"作左幾首曲，個人覺得還可以，都係普通流行曲feel，但就覺得作詞好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實係咁，小弟讀緊大學，成日聽人講大學係一個俾你發掘你既興趣既地方，而我一直都對音樂幾有興趣，還掂有時間，想嘗試係呢方面試下，玩左幾年樂器一直都係彈人地d歌，於是就想的起心肝嘗試下自己作曲，唔好諗會唔會成功，就算我自己作到首歌，我自己都好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲打有類近既經驗或者做緊同樣既野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依加算係作左幾首曲，其實唔知首歌o唔ok，自己聽落都ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，試過俾朋友聽都話ok wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 實質其實唔知好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，有冇巴絲打有同樣既經驗可以分享俾小弟聽下，例如下一步可以繼續點樣做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93fd322b34f810e4a29913b0af72caecbc0a1d68","tid":186283,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T05:58:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9548ad21d27c9d6d9479958c250a8d3be5b8609","tid":186283,"uid":98041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T06:17:18.000Z","msg":"搵人唱<br />\n放上utube<br />\n好似話試下send歌去唱片公司同咩作曲歌協會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"445a99aa19952e32ac35982926987d7a07be86e7","tid":186283,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T07:25:45.000Z","msg":"<